Dentistry.aboutUs:
OUR CLINIC MAKES YOUR HIGHEST SAFETY STANDARDS
The clinic uses 5 stages of sterilization of instruments.
The settings are processed after each reception.
All removable elements and tips are sterilized at 134 degrees Celsius.

A complex approach!
We consider the state of the oral cavity of each of our patients in close connection with the state of the whole organism.
We do a full-fledged diagnosis and offer ideal solutions to a complex of problems, thereby reducing the time and cost of treatment.

Vidnova dentistry has a large staff of leading specialists and each doctor is in love with his work.
They are real dental perfectionists, their mission is to make your smile perfect.
